]},{"name":"Nan","meanings":["Originally a pet form of   Ann   (for the initial <i>N-</i>,  compare  Ned  ). It is now also widely used as a short form of   Nancy ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Lady, Anne Cortney was born about 1141, in Winwick, Northamptonshire, England as the daughter of John Cortney. She married Sir, Thomas Andrews , I about 1162, in Northamptonshire, England. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. She died about 1166, in her hometown, at the age of 27."},"et":{"Abt 1141–about 1166":"umbes 1141–umbes 1166","1141–1166":"1141–1166","1139–1164":"1139–1164","1163–1200":"1163–1200","1165–Male":"1165–Surnud","1115–Male":"1115–Surnud","about 1162":"umbes 1162","1165":"1165","1164":"1164","1163":"1163","1141":"1141","Abt 1141":"umbes 1141","1139":"1139","1115":"1115","1200":"1200","Abt 1165":"umbes 1165","1166":"1166","about 1166":"umbes 1166","about 1164":"umbes 1164","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Winwick, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Winwick, Northamptonshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Winwick, Northamptonshire, England":"Winwick, Northamptonshire, England"},"fi":{"Abt 1141–about 1166":"noin 1141–noin 1166","1141–1166":"1141–1166","1139–1164":"1139–1164","1163–1200":"1163–1200","1165–Male":"1165–Kuollut","1115–Male":"1115–Kuollut","about 1162":"noin 1162","1165":"1165","1164":"1164","1163":"1163","1141":"1141","Abt 1141":"noin 1141","1139":"1139","1115":"1115","1200":"1200","Abt 1165":"noin 1165","1166":"1166","about 1166":"noin 1166","about 1164":"noin 1164","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Winwick, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Winwick, Northamptonshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Winwick, Northamptonshire, England":"Winwick, Northamptonshire, England"},"fr":{"Abt 1141–about 1166":"environ 1141–environ 1166","1141–1166":"1141–1166","1139–1164":"1139–1164","1163–1200":"1163–1200","1165–Male":"1165–Décédé","1115–Male":"1115–Décédé","about 1162":"environ 1162","1165":